## LRUCache.evictAll() method

Evicts all items from the cache, calling the eviction callback on each item.

Use \[\[clear\]\] to remove all items without calling the eviction callback.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
evictAll(): void;
```
<b>Returns:</b>

void
